{"tid":360106,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實粵語最強大係組合到好多個音，可善加利用？","createTime":"2017-08-15T04:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T14:52:22.000Z","uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9bf3979d18db58cd25826c40ef4fb83fd2ee64","tid":360106,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2F&d=aQcvaE3XEPnkTHhprgLkAqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=b74efe75\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/</a><br />\n用依個簡聲母韻母查字，會發覺極大多數粵語系統發到既音都係無字<br />\n就算有字，多數亦可能只有一兩個聲調<br />\n<br />\n直覺話我知依個係粵語潛在優勢<br />\n其實粵語聲韻調配搭變化遠比普通話多<br />\n日常生活我地都成日講無字寫既音，但因為無得寫好多人就覺得俗<br />\n<br />\n難度係就算搵左一個所謂正字比個音，但因為少人識少人用一樣唔會普及<br />\n<br />\n好似徐冰咁自創個造字系統，以字既某部份代表聲韻調，組合而成一個新字，但要學先明不如打返英文符號加數字好過"},{"pid":"08270148585a333c4f82a4d2f3aae6e0fa32b5ec","tid":360106,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed935c0adcd2efaa2955f26e79d1231f39b0b9a","tid":360106,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"Er...."}]}